<section id="faq">
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How long does a typical project take?</h3>
        <p>
            Simple websites can be completed in 2-4 weeks. Web applications typically 
            take 8-16 weeks depending on complexity. We'll establish a clear timeline 
            during the planning phase.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you work with clients remotely?</h3>
        <p>
            Yes! I work with clients worldwide. Most communication happens via email, 
            video calls, and project management tools.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What if I need changes after launch?</h3>
        <p>
            You get one full year of complimentary technical support for bug fixes 
            and minor adjustments. For new features or major changes, we can discuss 
            ongoing maintenance packages.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can you work with my existing code/team?</h3>
        <p>
            Absolutely! I can jump into existing projects, review code, add features, 
            or collaborate with your current development team.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What technologies do you work with?</h3>
        <p>
            I specialize in JavaScript/TypeScript (React, Vue, Node.js), Python, 
            static site generators (Eleventy, Next.js), and modern web technologies. 
            I choose the best tools for your specific needs.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
